Matthew Lewis (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matthew_Lewis_(actor) 0 Matthew David Lewis (born 27 June 1989) is an English film, television and stage actor, best known for playing Neville Longbottom in the Harry Potter films, Jamie Bradley in The Syndicate and Corporal Gordon "Towerblock" House in the BBC Three comedy drama Bluestone 42.
